<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٥٦٥ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ زِيَادِ بْنِ عِلَاقَةَ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ جَرِيرًا <span class="special">﵁</span> يَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بَايَعْتُ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>،<span class="c5"> فَاشْتَرَطَ عَلَيَّ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَالنُّصْحِ لِكُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>